Package: NMOF
Type: Package
Title: Numerical Methods and Optimization in Finance
Version: 0.14-1
Date: 2011-07-21
Author: Enrico Schumann
Author@R: person("Enrico", "Schumann", email = "enricoschumann@yahoo.de")
Maintainer: Enrico Schumann <enricoschumann@yahoo.de>
Suggests: MASS, quadprog, RUnit
Description: Functions, examples and data from the book 'Numerical Methods and Optimization in Finance' by M. Gilli, D. Maringer and E. Schumann. The package contains, in particular, several functions for heuristic optimisation (eg, Differential Evolution, Genetic Algorithms or Threshold Accepting).
